vulnerabilities.suggested_fix:
Update the existing `PlayerSettings` struct instead of overwriting it. Ensure `lockedAmount` accumulates the new deposit.

```solidity
playerBalances[msg.sender] += amount;
playerSettings[msg.sender].lockedAmount += amount;
playerSettings[msg.sender].lockRecipient = msg.sender;
playerSettings[msg.sender].lockDuration = duration;
playerSettings[msg.sender].lockStartTime = block.timestamp;
```
